{
    "headline": "Perfect Mixed Greens",
    "name": "Perfect Mixed Greens",
    "description": "Fresh greens like collard, mustard, and turnip are boiled in a seasoned broth to make a savory, sweet side dish for fried chicken or baked pork chops.",
    "recipeCuisine": [
        "Southern"
